      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior still has a great shine, though there are a few minor rock chips on the front end and a small scuff on the driver-side door handle. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the upholstery. It runs reliably and handles well, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable car that has been treated with care.",
